                    p.reservation__calculate-add-services-txt Сбор за дополнительные услуги
                        .reservation__calculate-add-services-txt-ellipse
                            span.reservation__calculate-add-services-txt-i i
                    p.reservation__calculate-add-services-price 300₽
                .reservation__calculate-sum
                    h2.reservation__calculate-sum-txt Итого
                    h2.reservation__calculate-sum-price 38 081₽
